8218-3969-1 }}</ref> * [[Vladimir Vranić]] (1896–1976), probability and statistics<ref>{{cite book|first1=Snješka|last1=Knežević|first2=Aleksander|last2=Laslo|title=Židovski Zagreb|year=2011|publisher=AGM, Židovska općina Zagreb|location=Zagreb|isbn=978-953-174-393-8|page=79}}</ref>
