f Hurwitz and the "Jewish Question" in German Academia|url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2FBF02986201|first=David E.|last=Rowe|author-link=David E. Rowe|journal=The Mathematical Intelligencer|volume=29|number=2|year=2007|doi=10.1007/BF02986201|issn=0343-6993}}</ref>}}
